<!--*********************************************
            Solution
**********************************************-->
<solution>
<p>We are looking for factors of $d{simplify} that add up to <m>-$c{simplify}</m>. The two factors are <m>-$a</m> and <m>-$b</m>.</p>
<p>The fully factored form is <m>$factoredExp{simplify}.</m></p>

</solution>
</problem>
